is real and it's moving.

00:06:25.380 --> 00:06:28.230
And these students are
absolutely phenomenal.

00:06:28.230 --> 00:06:29.820
So how does the program work?

00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:31.120
It's a pyramid structure.

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:32.420
It's a lot like the spelling bee.

00:06:32.420 --> 00:06:34.950
The students start at the
classroom level and then they move

00:06:34.950 --> 00:06:37.700
on to a school-wide competition,
and then they may have a regional

00:06:37.700 --> 00:06:39.270
or a state finals competition.

00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:42.680
And then they finally come to
D.C. to the national finals,

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.980
which are held here every spring.

00:06:44.980 --> 00:06:47.500
If you are an interested high
school student in the audience

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:49.770
