00:17:03.100 --> 00:17:05.900
"Lions" by Sandra McPherson.

00:17:05.900 --> 00:17:10.700
Lions don't need your help.

00:17:10.700 --> 00:17:13.490
In the Serengeti, for instance,

00:17:13.490 --> 00:17:18.090 position:56%
one thousand like the very rich hold
sway over more than Connecticut.

00:17:18.090 --> 00:17:21.440
The mane of the lion, like the
hooked jaw of the male salmon,

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:26.370
acts as a shield for defense and
is the gift of sexual selection.

00:17:26.370 --> 00:17:29.290
His eyes are fathomless amber.

00:17:29.290 --> 00:17:32.980
The lion is the most
social of the big cats.

00:17:32.980 --> 00:17:34.860
Pride members are affectionate
among themselves.

00:17:34.860 --> 00:17:36.540
They rub cheeks when they meet.

00:17:36.540 --> 00:17:38.000
They rest and hunt together.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:40.780
And cubs suckle indiscriminately.

00:17:40.780 --> 00:17:44.360
But strangers or members

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:47.110
of a neighboring pride
are not usually accepted.

00:17:47.110 --> 00:17:51.530
If a pride male meets a
strange female he may greet her

00:17:51.530 --> 00:17:55.590
in a friendly fashion
and even mate with her,

00:17:55.590 --> 00:17:58.530
but the pride females
will drive her off.

00:17:58.530 --> 00:18:01.760
Male lions, usually depicted
as indolent freeloaders

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:05.530
who let the lionesses do all the
hunting, are not mere parasites.

00:18:05.530 --> 00:18:10.510
They maintain the integrity
of the territory.

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:14.490
Lions eat communally but
completely lack table manners.

00:18:14.490 --> 00:18:16.250
Indeed, lions give the impression

00:18:16.250 --> 00:18:19.980
that their evolution toward a
social existence is incomplete,

00:18:19.980 --> 00:18:22.290
that cooperation in
achieving a task does not

00:18:22.290 --> 00:18:25.600
yet include the equal
division of the spoils.

00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:28.880
More bad news: lions
are not good parents.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:33.410
But prowess, that they have.

00:18:33.410 --> 00:18:35.820
Their courage comes
from being built,

00:18:35.820 --> 00:18:39.410
like an automobile, for power.

00:18:39.410 --> 00:18:47.950 position:56%
A visible lion is usually a safe
lion, but one should never feel safe

00:18:47.950 --> 00:18:56.490
because almost always there
is something one can't see.

00:18:56.490 --> 00:19:01.410
Given protection and power a
lion does not need to be clever.

00:19:01.410 --> 00:19:03.690
Now, lions are not
the most likable kind

00:19:03.690 --> 00:19:07.970
of animal unless you are
a certain type of person.

00:19:07.970 --> 00:19:11.820
That is, not necessarily leonine
in the sense of manly or ferocious,

00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:15.460
but one who wouldn't mind resting
twenty of twenty-four hours a day

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:18.300
and who is not beyond
stealing someone else's kill

00:19:18.300 --> 00:19:21.080
about half the time.

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:25.960
Lions are not my favorite kind
of animal, gazelles seem nicer,

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:29.860
[laughter] A zebra has his
own sort of appealing pathos,

00:19:29.860 --> 00:19:33.550
