sure prey for the lion.

00:19:33.550 --> 00:19:36.160
Lions have little to
offer the spirit.

00:19:36.160 --> 00:19:40.760
If we made of ourselves
parks and placed the lion

00:19:40.760 --> 00:19:46.770 position:56%
